Tony Czuczka talk with  Charlie Rose  about their new book, 
"Angela Merkel: A Chancellorship Forged in Crisis," and the 
future of Germany. ("Charlie Rose" airs weeknights on PBS and 
Bloomberg Television. Source: Charlie Rose)  Running Time: 09:16
 